      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CANYA FLAVOUR (8) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 1 last run (30.02) at this track. Capable of going well again. ADA TANGO (1) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (34.32) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. The form out of her last race has been franked. Should be in this for a long way. ZIPPING HOULIHAN (7) is generally an honest type in the frame at three of 12 starts but missed the placings last time when fifth (30.29) over 520m at this track. Tends to go well on this box draw. Will go close here with a clear run. BURNSIDE BOOKIE (3) was below best last time at this track (30.43) in a Grade 5, finishing a 7 length fourth. Already a winner from this draw.",
